# Title: Suspicious File Creation Activity From Fake Recycle.Bin Folder
# Author: X__Junior (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-07-12
# Level: high
# Description: Detects file write event from/to a fake recycle bin folder that is often used as a staging directory for malware
# MITRE Tactic: Persistence
# Tags: attack.persistence, attack.stealth
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/file/file_event/file_event_win_susp_recycle_bin_fake_exec.yml

Image IN ("*RECYCLERS.BIN\\*", "*RECYCLER.BIN\\*") OR TargetFilename IN ("*RECYCLERS.BIN\\*", "*RECYCLER.BIN\\*")